<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1436,1363,1529]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
Bees of this genus were found to have floral preferences restricted to one family or genus, especially 
<taxonomicName authorityName="G.T.Burnett" authorityYear="1835" box="[1285,1433,1433,1459]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Brassicaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[151,328,1468,1494]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Campanulaceae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="(Sedivy et al. 2008)" baseAuthorityName="Sedivy" baseAuthorityYear="2008" box="[382,781,1468,1494]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Ranunculaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">
Ranunculaceae (
<bibRefCitation author="Sedivy, C. &amp; Praz, C. J. &amp; Muller, A. &amp; Widmer, A. &amp; Dorn, S." box="[565,774,1468,1494]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" pagination="2487 - 2507" refId="ref107047" refString="Sedivy, C., Praz, C. J., Muller, A., Widmer, A. &amp; Dorn, S. (2008) Patterns of host-plant choice in bees of the genus Chelostoma: the constraint hypothesis of host-range evolution in bees. Evolution, 62, 2487 - 2507. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1558 - 5646.2008.00465. x" type="journal article" year="2008">
Sedivy 
<emphasis box="[651,707,1468,1494]" italics="true" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">et al.</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Very few flower records are available in our listed records below, but there seems to be a preference for 
<taxonomicName box="[659,836,1503,1529]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Campanulaceae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Praz" baseAuthorityYear="2017" box="[889,1016,1503,1529]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
